GOAL:
The consolidation of the power distribution network of the PS and administrative areas on the Meyrin site will improve the network reliability and availability, thanks to:
- Replacement of outdated equipment and unavailability of spare units (switchgears, transformers and power cables);
- Replacement of underdimensionned equipment not withstanding anymore the short circuit levels (switchgears and power cables);
- Response to client needs requiring to adapt and/or extend the network.

